<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-12-28T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-12-28T18:00:00-05:00" n="492" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d492">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">882.24/47 Suppl: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Chargé in Liberia</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Hibbard</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-12-28T19:00:00-04:00">December
                                    28, 1942—7 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>321. Your 401, December 4. You may communicate the following message to
                            President Barclay from President Roosevelt: <quote rend="blockquote">
                                <p>“I deeply appreciate the decision of the Republic of Liberia to
                                    adopt a policy of full collaboration with the United Nations and
                                    extend my hearty felicitations on the determination of your
                                    Government to lend its aid in combatting and destroying the Axis
                                    aggressors. Liberia’s contribution to the common cause will be
                                    warmly welcomed.”</p>
                            </quote>
                        </p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                </body></text></TEI>